  "articleContent": "<div>\n<div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\">She is favored by fate under one name, and swept away by it in another.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\">Yet never once has she been defeated, nor has she ever yielded.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"2\" data-line=\"true\">Now, witness the defiant Priestess. Witness what keeps her striding forward, never to look back. Witness how she walks the intricate web of destiny and becomes the only answer.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"2\" data-line=\"true\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1777219200000/9aw8v2x6ofpfw164fg-1777278587172.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"2\" data-line=\"true\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1777219200000/8gpbknxkrao1zs3jyu-1777278607589.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"8890\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1777219200000/6ki5nt9wnjvff4fluf-1777278621693.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"14128\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1777219200000/swx5rqgkv1idgnd9y1-1777278634280.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"15640\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
